description: The SPDR DoubleLine Emerging Markets Fixed Income ETF seeks to provide high total return from current income and capital appreciationProvides actively managed exposure to emerging market fixed income securitiesManaged by DoubleLine’s Emerging Market Fixed Income team who has worked together since 1999 and follows a 5 step investment process that combines bottom-up research with sovereign macro overlaysIn allocating investments among various emerging market countries, the team at Doubleline attempts to analyze internal political, market and economic factors
